data.description: FALL IN LOVE with this 10 acre paradise! Amazing water view of your very own deep, private stocked pond spanning nearly 2 acres. Relax in rural bliss while casting a line out from the dock or boat and catch immediately. With 2 homes, 2 septic tanks, and an RV hookup, you can accommodate generations of family or even rent for income. 3 bed 2 bath main home has a new roof and features level 3 granite countertops on custom cabinets, newer stainless appliances, and tiled backsplash. Guest home is approx 650 sqft self contained with 2 bed 1 bath and is handicap accessible with a complete kitchen, granite countertops, WD hookup, and walk in tiled shower. Set up for all your rural needs with a clean and dry storm shelter, oversized carport, 2 storages, and a chicken coop. Come see it in person!
